sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant H as UrlController
    participant S as UrlService
    participant K as UrlCache
    participant D as H2 Database

    C->>H: GET /{alias}
    H->>S: resolveRedirect(alias)
    S->>K: Lookup alias
    alt cache hit
        K-->>S: long URL
        S->>D: Increment access count (locked row)
    else cache miss
        S->>D: SELECT alias
        D-->>S: row
        S->>K: Populate cache
        S->>D: Increment access count (locked row)
    end
    S-->>H: long URL
    H-->>C: 302 Found
